title: Font ID please - Similar to Miso, FF Netto, VAG Rounded or Gravur Condensed but not any of them
content:
Can anybody identify this font? Thanks.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20121215160722im_/http:/typophile.com/files/young_6504.jpg)
author: Cyberdave

comments.content:
It looks like ink-pen lettering using a guide or template. Are you sure this is a font? It even looks like it has inkspread on the paper.

- Mike Yanega

I'm not sure if it's a font, but I like it. I found it on a press ad. The body copy used under it was VAG Rounded. The only place this font was used was in the Header, so maybe it's a custom font.

The inkspread effect around it is because I have scanned it in and converted it to Black & White.
